✔ Click Verify → Modal → Yes → status = 1
✔ Click Unverify → Modal → Yes → status = 0
✔ Click Inactive → Modal → Yes → status = 2

💡 Pro Laravel tip (very important for interviews):

Use constants in model instead of numbers.

const UNVERIFIED = 0;
const VERIFIED = 1;
const INACTIVE = 2;

Then:

if($user->status == User::VERIFIED)

This is industry best practice.
